# Irish: 2,261
# Guatemalan: 1,505
# American (United States): 1,111
# German: 1,087
# Mexican: 911
# English: 869
# Puerto Rican: 648
# French: 517
# Peruvian: 476

About one-third of survey respondents who reported ancestry reported multiple ancestries. Sixteen percent didn&#x27;t report ancestry or their answer was unclassified in one of the groups the Census Bureau listed.

==== Fastest growing nationalities ====
The 10 nationalities that grew fastest in Mamaroneck Village from 2010 to 2019 were:

